data.description: This RARE find in West Knoxville's Hampton Hall is extremely convenient, nicely updated, move-in ready, and awaiting its new owner!  You'll be impressed with the upgrades and updates throughout including new kitchen with farmhouse sink, butcher block island, new fixtures throughout, new flooring throughout main level, new primary bathroom walk-in shower, composite decking (covered and uncovered), new guest bath walk-in shower, and so much more.  This home features over 3,000 SF with 4 bedrooms, oversized bonus room, formal den, formal dining room plus large yet cozy living room and breakfast room. Seller offering a $3,000 carpet allowance with an acceptable offer. All HVAC ducts cleaned in January 2024.  Seller requests advanced notice for showings!
